00:09:12.558 --> 00:09:15.033
So I want to make sure
it's exactly the same bill.

00:09:15.033 --> 00:09:17.532
Now not only that, I want you
to take the paper clip

00:09:17.532 --> 00:09:19.732
and put it around the bill.

00:09:19.732 --> 00:09:22.338
So even if nobody comes onstage
and switches the bill,

00:09:22.338 --> 00:09:25.617
I don't have enough time
to go open the bill and close it

00:09:25.617 --> 00:09:27.256
and see what I don't want to see.

00:09:27.280 --> 00:09:28.441
Is that fair?

00:09:28.441 --> 00:09:30.228
Now you can give me the marker back.

00:09:30.228 --> 00:09:32.488
And just like that, very clearly,

00:09:32.488 --> 00:09:35.507
I want to make sure that
we place this in full view

00:09:35.507 --> 00:09:40.693
from the beginning of this experience

00:09:40.693 --> 00:09:43.174
and to make sure that everyone
is going to see it,

00:09:43.174 --> 00:09:46.939
