HG: The two. And after the two?

00:12:23.633 --> 00:12:24.875
Audience member 4: Three.

00:12:24.875 --> 00:12:26.518
HG: Three, and after?

00:12:26.518 --> 00:12:28.484
Audience member 4: Three.
HG: Three.

00:12:28.484 --> 00:12:30.540
Audience member 4: Seven.
HG: Seven.

00:12:30.540 --> 00:12:32.274
Audience member 4: Four.
HG: Four.

00:12:32.274 --> 00:12:34.788
Audience member 4: Two.
HG: Two, and?

00:12:34.788 --> 00:12:36.718
Audience member 4: Q.

00:12:36.718 --> 00:12:40.590
HG: Q like in queen?

00:12:40.590 --> 00:12:42.280
(Applause)

00:12:42.280 --> 00:12:43.590
The queen of clubs!

00:12:43.590 --> 00:12:47.420
All the cards in order, just for you.

00:12:47.420 --> 00:12:48.716
